        "text": "Systems thinking inspires us to write, share, and aggregate small graphs in order to discover larger ones. We compose these products of our imagination as graph-shaped \"poems\" in the style of Haiku. Wiki's property graph representation joins tables and trees in the space right behind the glass and travels freely within our federation. A thematic sketch, such as \"organizing for action,\" makes purposeful authoring a matter of choosing relations from a menu. Nodes that match are highlighted. Nodes that don't match invite another composition that brings these ideas together."
